nodes.bodyText:
There is now an annotation: @RemoveOnNextMajorRelease, perhaps that annotation can take the place of this comment?
IMO it might make sense to add a "default" string to that annotation that we can use as a comment. Hence you could do something like:
@RemoveOnNextMajorRelease("Anonymous inner class can be inlined")

